MENU_PKG_GNUSTEP
  Here you'll find options for GNUstep.

SDECFG_PKG_GNUSTEP_CORE_PREFIX
  The prefix all GNUstep related packages will be installed into. The T2
  default is an empty string (""), so that a Mac OS X top-level directory
  structure such as /Library, /System and /Application is used.
